data.description: Welcome to the quiet tree-lined 2331 Mountain View Drive in beautiful Concord.   This family-friendly neighborhood has easy access to everything. Close to scenic downtown, BART, parks, schools, shopping, and easy freeway access. This charming 3 bed 2 bath hosts 1,349 sq ft of living space and welcoming outdoor spaces for lounging and entertaining. A number of upgrades were made 2023 including a newly remodeled oversized main bedroom with attached bath, walk-in closet, skylights, and slider. New water-resistant engineered hardwood flooring throughout the home, updated plumbing including the sewer lateral line, and all new appliances. The open-concept living space boasts natural light and a cozy eat-in kitchen with granite counters. Laundry room inside home with attached garage and newer water heater.
